The younger brother of Kenneth Omeruo has signed on the dotted line in Lithuania. Speaking the London base agent Akorede Hutman, who facilitated the deal,National Daily gathered.
“It is true that he has signed and this has caused great celebration for the Omeruo family .
After considering the different options on the table, we decided to sign with Palanga because the club showed how serious they were about affing quality to the squad
. The club presented a good offer for a player of his pedigree so let us see how it goes in the first year of his contract and then review to see how things are going.
